        <button class="faq-question" onclick="this.parentElement.classList.toggle('open')">
          What is Teamwork Commerce?
          <span class="faq-icon"><i class="ti ti-plus"></i></span>
        </button>
        <div class="faq-answer">
          <p>Teamwork Commerce is a global, AI-enabled retail platform that natively integrates enterprise POS, OMS, Inventory Management, RFID, and AI (121 Commerce) into one system. It powers 30,000+ terminals across 40+ countries with 99.99% uptime, serving mid-market and enterprise retailers in fashion, footwear, stadiums, museums, jewelry, and specialty retail.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-item">
        <button class="faq-question" onclick="this.parentElement.classList.toggle('open')">
          How does Teamwork Commerce handle offline transactions?
          <span class="faq-icon"><i class="ti ti-plus"></i></span>
        </button>
        <div class="faq-answer">
          <p>Teamwork Commerce uses Store-and-Forward technology that keeps the POS fully functional during network outages. Transaction data is encrypted and stored locally on the iOS device, then automatically synced to Cloud HQ once connectivity is restored — preventing lost sales and data gaps.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-item">
        <button class="faq-question" onclick="this.parentElement.classList.toggle('open')">
          What makes the RFID solution different from competitors?
          <span class="faq-icon"><i class="ti ti-plus"></i></span>
        </button>
        <div class="faq-answer">
          <p>Teamwork Commerce offers the industry's only native end-to-end RFID stack — no third-party middleware required. It covers source tagging, RFID-enabled checkout (scan an entire basket in one tap), real-time item-level tracking, loss prevention with EAS integration, and full-store cycle counts in minutes. This delivers 99.9% inventory accuracy.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-item">
        <button class="faq-question" onclick="this.parentElement.classList.toggle('open')">
          What is 121 Commerce?
          <span class="faq-icon"><i class="ti ti-plus"></i></span>
        </button>
        <div class="faq-answer">
          <p>121 Commerce is what Plus unlocks at the point of sale on our Product Experience Platform (PXP) and Customer Experience Platform (CXP) — not a separate product. It surfaces real-time product knowledge, customer history, and intelligent recommendations at every touchpoint, making every associate as knowledgeable as your best.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-item">
        <button class="faq-question" onclick="this.parentElement.classList.toggle('open')">
          Is Teamwork Commerce SOC 2 compliant?
          <span class="faq-icon"><i class="ti ti-plus"></i></span>
        </button>
        <div class="faq-answer">
          <p>Yes. Teamwork Commerce maintains SOC 2 Type 2 compliance and is fully GDPR and PCI DSS compliant. The platform also supports fiscal compliance standards including NF525 (France) and TSE (Germany) across 40+ countries.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-item">
        <button class="faq-question" onclick="this.parentElement.classList.toggle('open')">
          How long does deployment take?
          <span class="faq-icon"><i class="ti ti-plus"></i></span>
        </button>
        <div class="faq-answer">
          <p>Teamwork Commerce supports guided, phased rollouts from single-store pilots to global fleet deployments. The design-led UI reduces associate training to under 30 minutes, and the dedicated service team manages every implementation directly — no third-party outsourcing. Retailers have gone live with new associates on registers in as little as 5 minutes.</p>
